1760:Drivers/STM32H7xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32h7xx_ll_adc.h ****   * @note   The different literal definitions of ADC channels are:
1761:Drivers/STM32H7xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32h7xx_ll_adc.h ****   *         - ADC internal channel:
