2830:Drivers/STM32H7xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32h7xx_ll_adc.h ****   *         @ref LL_ADC_StartCalibration().
2831:Drivers/STM32H7xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32h7xx_ll_adc.h ****   * @note   For devices with differential mode available:
