2838:Drivers/STM32H7xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32h7xx_ll_adc.h ****   *         single-ended and differential modes
2839:Drivers/STM32H7xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32h7xx_ll_adc.h ****   *         (calibration factor can be specified only once).
