6331:Drivers/STM32H7xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32h7xx_ll_adc.h ****   *           are done from 1 trigger)
6332:Drivers/STM32H7xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32h7xx_ll_adc.h ****   *         - discontinuous mode (each conversion of oversampling ratio
