1879:Drivers/STM32H7xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h7xx_hal_adc.c ****   *          2. then enable the EOSMP interrupt with macro __HAL_ADC_ENABLE_IT(hadc, ADC_IT_EOSMP)
